snippet.title: NullStar Promo
snippet.description:
NullStar is the first game from indie studio Pizza Blade Games.
https://pizzabladegames.com

Our hero awakens with the need to run, but why? Get to the end of this finite runner to unlock the mystery and our hero's full potential.

NO ADS! A free game with no ads, no daily rewards, no meaningless trinkets. Just arcade-style action.
